title: Sample Gallery
description:
This is an example of what one of our galleries look like. All that you need to do is upload a spreadsheet of students' names and links to their song maker creations, and the site does the rest. You can spin up a gallery just like this for your students in only a few minutes!
Notice that the thumbnail images are not generic. Each student's actual composition is displayed on the website so that everyone in your school community can get a bird's eye view of the astounding creativity of our students.
